Preheat the oven to 200C/400F/Gas 6.In a small ovenproof non-stick frying pan, heat the olive oil and butter together and saut√© the onion until soft, but not coloured.Add the tomato and peas and season with salt and freshly ground black pepper.Pour over the eggs and cheese and cook over a low/medium heat until the base is set.Transfer to the oven for 8-10 minutes, or until cooked through.To serve, scatter with mint.